<seg id="2">AN Argentine widow spent days in her late husband's tomb, setting up a bed, internet access and even a small cooker next to his coffin, officials said Thursday.</seg>
<seg id="3">Police found Adriana Villareal had carried out some work in the tomb holding her husband's coffin.</seg>
