<seg id="8">Ms. Symon's film illustrates bluntly the Tuareg people's unmet needs for education and medical care in Mali, one of five countries into which they have been divided; the scarcity of water; and the fading away of their livelihood, the trans-Saharan caravan trade.</seg>
