<seg id="21">I thought I'd meet up with him for a few hours but we went to a bar and just chatted nonstop.</seg>
<seg id="22">Then we went to a restaurant at Southbank ... it ended up being a seven-hour date.</seg>
<seg id="23">He didn't even kiss me goodnight.</seg>
<seg id="24">I was a little bit disappointed but thought 'OK treat 'em mean, keep 'em keen'.</seg>
<seg id="25">Despite living in separate states, they've since caught up five times, including a date at Sea World.</seg>
<seg id="26">Sydney violinist Saraya Beric performing.</seg>
<seg id="27">Picture: Billy Joe.</seg>
<seg id="28">He's met my mum and I've met his.</seg>
<seg id="29">It's really fast moving.</seg>
