<seg id="35">We've talked about marriage but just jokingly.</seg>
<seg id="36">It's really funny because we've only been dating a month.</seg>
<seg id="37">He makes me laugh.</seg>
<seg id="38">Peter, who's been single for about three years, said he had just joined Tinder to make friends.</seg>
