<seg id="11">The Syrian military, overstretched by the civil war, has not retaliated, and it was not clear whether the embattled Syrian leader would choose to take action this time.</seg>
<seg id="12">Assad may decide to again let the Israeli attack slide, particularly when his army has the upper hand on the battlefield inside Syria.</seg>
