<seg id="1">Uk weather: Wild weather returns with 60mph gales, heavy rain and risk of flooding on washout weekend</seg>
<seg id="2">Met Office issues warnings for London and southern and eastern counties</seg>
<seg id="3">Gusts of up to 60mph predicted in parts of Wales</seg>
<seg id="4">Areas battered by St Jude storm to bear the brunt for a second time</seg>
<seg id="5">By Lizzie Parry and Lizzie Edmonds</seg>
<seg id="6">Swathes of the UK have been warned to expect flooding this weekend as mother nature unleashes a second barrage of stormy weather.</seg>
<seg id="7">The Met Office has issued a warning for southern England, alerting people to the risk of localised flooding today and on Sunday as heavy rain hits the coast.</seg>
