<seg id="19">Calling in an ambassador is a strong diplomatic step, and the revelations and swift response threaten to increase tensions in the relationship between the two countries at a time when Prime Minister Tony Abbott is seeking hose down ill-feeling in Indonesia from his electioneering over asylum seekers.</seg>
