<seg id="4">Earlier in the week Smith was summoned to Clarence House for a meeting with Prince Charles - and overnight the usually unflappable Melbourne Storm skipper had to back up at the home of Manchester United for a catch-up with the "other" Prince of England, David Beckham.</seg>
<seg id="5">Throw in some of the biggest names in world football in Ryan Giggs, Rio Ferdinand, Wayne Rooney, Robin van Persie and Michael Carrick, and Smith along with fellow Kangaroos Paul Gallen and Johnathan Thurston had a day out at Old Trafford they will probably never forget.</seg>
