<seg id="22">We were in Sydney all that week and it was like what we'd call a Champions League final.</seg>
<seg id="23">Kangaroos five-eighth Johnathan Thurston swaps jerseys with Manchester United icon Ryan Giggs.</seg>
<seg id="24">Australia takes on Fiji at Langtree Park on Saturday night but Smith said taking time out of their preparations for this once in a lifetime opportunity was well worth it.</seg>
<seg id="25">"It is nice to see that guys who play in such a huge sporting club know a fair bit about our game as well," Smith said.</seg>
